'''''Shuga''''', izwi kandi ku izina rya '''''MTV Shuga'''''<ref>https://www.thecompassforsbc.org/project-examples/shuga-television-series</ref>, ni urukurikirane rw'ikinamico rwa televiziyo rwatangajwe bwa mbere mu Gushyingo 2009 kuri MTV Base mu rwego rwo kwitwa "MTV staying alive Ignite!"<ref>https://www.thecompassforsbc.org/sbcc-spotlights/mtv-shuga</ref> . Ibice byayo bibiri byambere byahawe inshingano na MTV Networks Africa ifatanije na MTV Staying Alive Foundation<ref>https://www.prepwatch.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/MTV-Shuga-Fact-Sheet.pdf</ref>, PEPFAR, Ubufatanye bw’umuryango urwanya virusi itera SIDA (HFG) na Guverinoma ya [[Kenya]], mu rwego rwo gukwirakwiza ubutumwa bugamije gukwirakwiza ubutumwa ku myitwarire yimibonano mpuzabitsina no kwihangana<ref>https://www.comminit.com/healthafrica/content/shuga-television-series</ref>

Iyi filime yaje gukundwa cyane kandi yerekanwa mu bihugu 40 bitandukanye bya Afurika mbere yuko isohoka ku rwego mpuzamahanga kuri televiziyo zirenga 70<ref>https://www.africancelebs.com/mtv-shuga-tv-series/</ref>.  Ikinamico yatekerezaga ko ari urukurikirane ruvuguruzanya cyane nabasekuruza bakuru ba Kenya kuko rwarimo amashusho amwe yarimo ibintu byerekeranye n'igitsina<ref>https://www.owlapps.net/owlapps_apps/articles?id=34920815&lang=en</ref>.  Yabonye igihembo cya Zahabu muri Gicurasi 2010 mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga ry’itangazamakuru ryabereye i Hamburg mu [[Budage]] mu cyiciro cy’ubuzima rusange  kubera kwibanda ku rukundo, amarangamutima, n’imyitwarire y’imibonano mpuzabitsina mu rubyiruko rwo muri [[Kenya]]<ref>https://www.netflixtvseries.com/tv/99108/mtv-shuga</ref>. 

== MTV Shuga (2020) ==
Kubera icyorezo cya Coronavirus, Shuga yagiye mu gitaramo gito cya nijoro cyiswe MTV Shuga Alone Together kigaragaza ibibazo bya Coronavirus ku ya 20 Mata 2020<ref>https://www.researchgate.net/publication/324569914_A_THEMATIC_ANALYSIS_OF_MTV_SHUGA_DOWN_SOUTH_DRAMA_SERIES</ref>. Iki gitaramo cyagombaga gutambuka amajoro 65 kandi abayishyigikiye barimo [[Umuryango w’Abibumye|Umuryango w’abibumbye]] <ref>https://www.togetherforgirls.org/secrets-mtv-shugas-success/</ref>.  Urukurikirane rushingiye muri [[Nijeriya]], [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'epfo, [[Kenya]] na [[Kote Divuwari|Côte D'Ivoire]] kandi inkuru isobanurwa n'ibiganiro kumurongo hagati yabantu nyamukuru<ref>https://www.theguardian.com/global-development/2015/nov/30/shuga-mtv-african-tv-show-safe-sex-hiv</ref>. Inyandiko yanditswe na Tunde Aladese <ref>https://allnigeriainfo.ng/shuga-a-sensational-tv-series/</ref> na Nkiru Njoku .  Nibo banditsi bakuru kuri iki gitaramo kandi banayoboye ibice. Gufata amashusho, kumurika no kwisiga byakozwe nabakinnyi ubwabo<ref>https://republic.com.ng/october-november-2019/remarkable-strides-of-mtv-shuga/</ref>.

